Report and Dashboard Folders

Create reports and dashboards right from the Analytics tab. Rather than opening multiple tabs, you can stay in one app and create the analytics you want.

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Group, Enterprise, Professional, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.

To create reports and dashboards on the Analytics tab:
Enhanced Folder Sharing
Run Reports AND Create and Customize Dashboards

From the Analytics tab, click the Create button. Options to create a report, dashboard, and folder appear within its menu. For example, from the menu, click Dashboard, and it brings up the wizard for a new dashboard.

When you finish, use the navigation breadcrumb to return home.
title: Creating Reports and Dashboards on Salesforce Analytics Tab
